209</span> of the Holy Word') was apparently a great doctor and
confounder of heresies.

<span id="fn_945"></span>[209:1](sbe2318.htm#fr_990.md) See above, § 95.

<span id="fn_946"></span>[209:2](sbe2318.htm#fr_991.md) Possibly the eponym
