<span id="fn_1021"></span>[226:3](sbe2318.htm#fr_1078.md) Saoshya*nt*'s
mother.

<span id="fn_1022"></span>[226:4](sbe2318.htm#fr_1079.md) Cf. Vend. XIX, 5,
