227</span> Thraêtaona, as Turan and Iran were inherited by Tûra and
Airyu. Selm's heritage was Rûm, that is to say, Europa and Western Asia.

<span id="fn_1025"></span>[227:1](sbe2318.htm#fr_1082.md) China (Bund. XV,
29).

<span id="fn_1026"></span>[227:2](sbe2318.htm#fr_1083.md) Perhaps the Dahae
