<span id="fn_1027"></span>[227:3](sbe2318.htm#fr_1084.md) From the first
man to the last.

<span id="fn_1028"></span>[228:1](sbe2318.htm#fr_1085.md) Itinerant priests
are received here.

<span id="fn_1029"></span>[228:2](sbe2318.htm#fr_1086.md) Doubtful.

<span id="fn_1030"></span>[228:3](sbe2318.htm#fr_1087.md) Cf. [p.
198](#page_198), note [1](#fn_887.md).

<span id="fn_1031"></span>[228:4](sbe2318.htm#fr_1088.md) The
Paoiryô-*t*kaê*s*as; see [p. 180](#page_180), note [1](#fn_810.md).

<span id="fn_1032"></span>[228:5](sbe2318.htm#fr_1090.md) For the triumph
